        <section class="page-header" data-pattern="page-header-fallback" data-source-doc-id="components-pageheader--docs" data-fallback-reason="PageHeader docs exist but no primitive contract is registered yet.">
          <h1>中医药后台管理首页</h1>
          <p>按 resolver 输出组合 Elements primitives，Table 和 Chart 明确作为 fallback。</p>
